# Q2. NodePort

- Reconfigure the existing deployment **front-end** in namespace **spline-reticulator** to expose **80/tcp** of the existing container **nginx**.
- Create a new service named **front-end-svc** exposing the container port **80/tcp**
- configure the new service to also expose the individual pod via a **NodePort**.

---

환경설정

kubectl create ns spline-reticulator

kubectl create deploy front-end --image=nginx --namespace=spline-reticulator
